// Package stdlib is a collection of cty tions that are expected to be// generally useful, and are thus factored out into this shared library in// the hope thay-using applications will have consistent behavior when// using these tions.//// See the parent package "tion" for more information on purpose// and usage of tions.//// This package contains both Go tions, which provide convenient access// to call the tions from Go code, and the tion objects themselves.// The latter follow the naming scheme of appending "" to the end of// the tion name.package stdlib